Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.90,0:01:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你们照顾这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子很信任你们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.71,0:01:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法传递的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.71,0:01:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法相互理解的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.13,0:01:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法完成的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.68,0:01:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有着必须完成的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够完成吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.38,0:01:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.01,0:01:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要送姐姐一份礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.95,0:02:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人类 精灵 以及两者之间的种族
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.16,0:02:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都能平等生活的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.34,0:02:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个没有歧视的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.45,0:02:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有尤安和库拉特斯在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.67,0:02:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.60,0:02:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.10,0:02:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.95,0:02:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要守护这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.02,0:02:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护这片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.21,0:02:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.59,0:02:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.83,0:02:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.35,0:02:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.94,0:03:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾立足于凝聚天光之地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝身处于开启的地狱门前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.46,0:03:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以光辉之神名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为堕落于地的污垢灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洒下制裁的圣光之雨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出袭吧 神之雷！ 愤怒神雷！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.10,0:03:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,审判！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.30,0:04:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她所期待的未来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都错了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里错…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.66,0:05:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.58,0:05:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都错了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.06,0:05:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我错了 你也错了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米特斯也错了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都犯下了无法挽回的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.66,0:05:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变强 我想变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.73,0:05:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算再怎么变强也不能代替她承受痛苦 这我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.74,0:05:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.16,0:05:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追求着无法实现的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挣扎 受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊德正是过去的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊德能不重蹈我的覆辙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不迷失方向地走下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去确认吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.11,0:06:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你儿子走的是什么样的路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够自由往来于特塞阿拉和希尔瓦兰特之间的次元通道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是了不起的遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.40,0:08:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要占领了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没必要冒险骑三趾鸵鸟去穿越次元扭曲空间了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提问～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直寻找的遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.12,0:08:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是精灵奥利津的封印吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这篇古文上记载着封印的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要找到解开封印的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让特塞阿拉和希尔瓦兰特和谐统和…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这么说的来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.01,0:09:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为文字变模糊了读不准嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣人也会犯错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦耶 迷糊巫女万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再说一遍试试
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.69,0:09:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是在夸你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可听不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利菲尔 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.18,0:09:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利菲尔 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.92,0:09:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.76,0:10:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 泽洛斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯蕾特不讨厌神子的身份吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然说为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不想自由地掌握自己的人生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.42,0:10:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很自由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.19,0:10:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我的身体被夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但心灵还是自由的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我会尽情地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和罗伊德 和大家在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然也要和泽洛斯在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且希望世界和大家都能变得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽洛斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害啊 柯蕾特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爷可是学不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.37,0:10:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.77,0:10:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到吃饭的时间了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是谁做饭来着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯蕾特 柯蕾特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.11,0:11:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子疼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.38,0:11:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.39,0:11:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 开动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐们应该快回来了 再等等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子饿过头快死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃啊 罗伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.17,0:11:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.29,0:11:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊德 在淑女们面前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:11:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能吃的规矩点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:11:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭菜合大家口味吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还担心不合大家口味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.17,0:12:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.01,0:12:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棒极了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.10,0:12:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米特斯 你简直是天才
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.06,0:12:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.63,0:12:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 这是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能成为我们的同伴真是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯蕾特不管做什么菜都放水果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉尼亚斯虽然会做饭 但是也已经吃腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.63,0:12:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过分 我再也不给你做饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 我胡说的 你的饭也很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.99,0:12:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:12:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师情况怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.30,0:13:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是奥泽特感冒的症状
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静养的话一星期就能痊愈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也难怪 旅途太辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 那可是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.01,0:13:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直连睡觉的时间都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.42,0:13:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有时间睡觉还不是因为你彻夜骚扰希尔瓦兰特的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为本大爷太帅了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都不愿放我走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.44,0:13:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.92,0:13:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事都麻烦你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的伤怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.70,0:13:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有点…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.79,0:14:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 吉尼亚斯和米特斯呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样姐姐就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然还精通草药 米斯特实在太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我的身体就算生病也不能看医生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.18,0:14:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂得很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.14,0:14:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算喝了泥浆水也不会闹肚子的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.23,0:14:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄潜入家畜的小屋偷走蛋类的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.13,0:14:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记被木棒殴打后的疼痛的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.96,0:15:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我一直有守护我的姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉尼亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没必要为此道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能怪那些歧视我们半精灵的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉尼亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.65,0:15:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在特塞阿拉出生成长的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后和还是婴儿的吉尼亚斯一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.98,0:16:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被抛弃在那个遗迹里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被精灵的母亲所忌讳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在另一个世界生活更能得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你母亲一定是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在希尔瓦兰特也没有半精灵的立足之地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.07,0:16:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱着吉尼亚斯 居无定所地四处漂泊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知经过了多少年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.98,0:16:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终到达的就是伊赛利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么吉尼亚斯和利菲尔小姐会和人类在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很讨厌人类哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很讨厌人类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也有像罗伊德那样的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.59,0:17:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是所有人都是坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 罗伊德不知道事实的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我隐瞒了身份
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.21,0:17:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是半精灵 而是精灵的姐弟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过这样不断地撒谎 终于得到了容身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚伪的容身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许他不是坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过罗伊德始终是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.23,0:17:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你也是明白的对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 一直以来都没有告诉罗伊德真相
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.35,0:18:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊德和你们之间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有着多年来建立起来的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.05,0:18:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只需要相信这份羁绊就行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.26,0:18:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直相信着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.25,0:18:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 正因为相信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才害怕被背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 说了些奇怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.02,0:18:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为吉尼亚斯和罗伊德的关系太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.49,0:18:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我有些羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米特斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.68,0:18:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次遇到和自己年龄相仿的半精灵朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:18:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.42,0:18:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.13,0:19:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉尼亚斯要是能和我一直在一起就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.03,0:19:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就在一起好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能当真吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以 我们不是朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.31,0:19:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我当真了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.53,0:19:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.15,0:19:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 罗伊德君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.85,0:19:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小鬼 那么轻易就当成自己人 真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说米特斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.54,0:20:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以一副狼狈的样子出现
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.08,0:20:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被马车撞飞受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.65,0:20:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想麻烦大家帮忙治疗 是这样来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.36,0:20:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克鲁西斯以及雷纳盖特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.39,0:20:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争可是还没结束的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以同伴的身份接近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.02,0:20:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出其不意攻其不备的小人还是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.32,0:20:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是那样也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起被信任的人背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不被信任的人更加痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.62,0:20:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让我失望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚持你一直以来的信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.73,0:20:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些话可是你告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.12,0:20:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有村民说 他们往山那边走去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.84,0:20:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.91,0:21:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你知道那个天使大人是你老爸的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是一直都没有坦白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并把你愚弄至今
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得火大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.26,0:21:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 突然问这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.17,0:21:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙对自己的儿子可是一直刀刃相向
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.17,0:21:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也很气愤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.39,0:21:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但库拉特斯应该有他自己的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.08,0:21:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也按照自己的想法走到了现在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.46,0:21:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天会和库拉特斯面对面地对话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.56,0:21:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 现在我只需要全力做好力所能及的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.14,0:22:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 真是奇怪的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.02,0:22:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 柯蕾特正等着呢 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.36,0:22:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.22,0:22:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力以赴…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.27,0:22:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些都是和本大爷无缘的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.61,0:22:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 塞雷斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.68,0:22:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 吉尼亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.32,0:22:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.58,0:22:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我和罗伊德吵架的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.41,0:22:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会帮哪一边呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.68,0:22:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.88,0:23:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来 尤安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.22,0:23:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.65,0:23:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要杀她
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.01,0:23:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.74,0:24:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.33,0:24:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.55,0:24:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.79,0:24:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能和你在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.47,0:24:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.93,0:24:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是一直都在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.11,0:24:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有姐姐的身边才是我存在的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.88,0:24:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果姐姐不在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.63,0:24:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我… 那我要上哪里去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.46,0:24:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天 一个没有歧视的世界会…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.88,0:24:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.53,0:24:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.12,0:25:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不行啦 普雷塞娅
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.32,0:25:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.00,0:26:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那对半精灵的姐弟 会成为我们的同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.69,0:26:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您又做梦了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.11,0:26:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.72,0:26:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这4000年来 让您独自一人承受着这份悲伤的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.96,0:26:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独自一人 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.97,0:26:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我普罗奈玛
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.85,0:26:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直守候在您身边
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.40,0:26:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱慕着您
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.48,0:26:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米特斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.28,0:26:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以这样称呼我的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.12,0:26:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有过去的同伴们
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.36,0:26:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.60,0:27:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.16,0:27:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米 米特斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.68,0:27:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是同类吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.55,0:27:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是被姐姐抚养长大的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.22,0:27:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.57,0:27:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉尼亚斯 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.08,0:27:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我的姐姐已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.47,0:27:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去姐姐的时候真的很悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.70,0:27:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在此之前我更不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.67,0:27:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀害姐姐的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.38,0:28:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你的话 应该会明白我的心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.17,0:28:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米特斯… 你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.04,0:28:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.41,0:28:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤 尤格德拉希尔
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.03,0:28:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.70,0:28:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要变成无机生命体
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.85,0:28:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身姿形态以及成长状态
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.97,0:28:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都能随意改变
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.01,0:28:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无机生命体…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.18,0:28:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是天使
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.46,0:28:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把所有生命体都变为天使的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.86,0:28:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是EX晶球的本质
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.44,0:28:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终的存在理由
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.17,0:29:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这力量能够实现什么
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.18,0:29:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉尼亚斯 利菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.76,0:29:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们应该能够明白
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.83,0:29:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉尼亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.44,0:29:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.24,0:29:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在正在用肮脏的脚 践踏一片不可侵犯的领域
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.26,0:29:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再让你说下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.26,0:29:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉尼亚斯 人会惧怕并且厌恶异类
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.51,0:29:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕不同于自己的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.73,0:29:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.14,0:30:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利加尔
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.06,0:30:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不同会招来歧视
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.48,0:30:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家只需要变成同类就行
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.23,0:30:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用EX晶球 把人类和精灵体内的血统清除
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.97,0:30:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这大地上的所有物种 都会变成无机生命体
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.28,0:30:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人类 精灵 以及两者之间的种族
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.81,0:30:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都能平等生活的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.85,0:30:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个没有歧视的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.43,0:30:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了制造这样一个千年王国
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.34,0:30:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才成立了克鲁西斯组织
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.11,0:30:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.84,0:30:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么消除血统也好 歧视也好
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.04,0:30:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在胡说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.68,0:30:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请说明白一点
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.42,0:30:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我应该有知情权
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.79,0:30:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉尼亚斯 利菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.54,0:30:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我邀请你们到我的王国来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.54,0:31:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们有这个资格
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.30,0:31:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤格德拉希尔
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.00,0:31:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.02,0:31:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.15,0:31:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤格德拉希尔是半精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.29,0:31:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和吉尼亚斯 和他都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.00,0:31:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.05,0:31:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师和吉尼亚斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.94,0:31:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.44,0:31:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是精灵 那是骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.81,0:31:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.15,0:31:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.06,0:31:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不明摆着的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.62,0:31:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们不想被赶出伊赛利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.96,0:31:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们不想被大家讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.41,0:31:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.59,0:31:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.72,0:32:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一直在一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.69,0:32:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.86,0:32:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊德 柯蕾特
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.66,0:32:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没办法相信人类
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.99,0:32:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的… 是我无法相信你们
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.36,0:32:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被藐视是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.25,0:32:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 希望你们明白
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.50,0:32:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉尼亚斯并没有罪
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.43,0:32:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我再三叮嘱不让他说出真相
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.11,0:32:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.88,0:32:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦说出去 就不能再做朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.10,0:32:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 这不是姐姐的错
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.57,0:32:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.12,0:32:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉尼亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.14,0:32:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.50,0:32:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说了 吉尼亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.44,0:32:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没有相信罗伊德和柯蕾特
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.96,0:32:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 所以才欺骗了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.84,0:33:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 罗伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.05,0:33:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许你不会再相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.27,0:33:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我真的一直都想和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.99,0:33:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只希望你能相信这个
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.08,0:33:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉尼亚斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.94,0:33:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.19,0:33:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉尼亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.78,0:33:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最痛苦的人 是不得不撒谎的你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.26,0:33:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在班里虽然是吊车尾的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.29,0:33:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但可不是连你的心情都不理解的白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.44,0:33:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我可是老师的学生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.67,0:33:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还愿意当我是老师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.87,0:33:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到现在除了这个还能怎么叫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.71,0:34:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止 从今往后 对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.69,0:34:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师还是老师 吉尼亚斯还是吉尼亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.26,0:34:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.10,0:34:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一直在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.30,0:34:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有个好学生啊 利菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.25,0:34:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.63,0:34:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说把所有生命体都变成天使？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.47,0:34:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做就能消除歧视？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.00,0:34:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此你要怎么制造EX晶球
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.24,0:34:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消减别人的生命去制造EX晶球
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.69,0:34:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的做法太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.29,0:34:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牺牲是改革的附属品
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.10,0:34:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那去寻找不会牺牲任何人的方法就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.34,0:34:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的方法不可能存在
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.15,0:34:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定有 一定会有方法的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.14,0:35:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想这样放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.96,0:35:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从出生的那一瞬间起 谁都有活下去的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.23,0:35:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类和精灵还有半精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.39,0:35:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要大家存在自我 就应该有活下去的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.65,0:35:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是理所当然的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.88,0:35:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.50,0:35:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.13,0:35:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库拉特斯你告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.46,0:35:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都驱逐半精灵并说那是灾厄的根源
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.76,0:35:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 我们到底应该何去何从
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.14,0:35:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米特斯 不能冲着库拉特斯泄愤
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.84,0:35:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道 这种事情今后还会不断地重复
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.52,0:35:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断地重复…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.14,0:35:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是约定了吗 米特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.78,0:35:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其绝望 不如寻找能够安静生活的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.54,0:35:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝望… 不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.98,0:35:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会放弃 所有人都选择沉默的话
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.05,0:36:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.19,0:36:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.36,0:36:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.19,0:36:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.37,0:36:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能找到不牺牲任何人的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.09,0:36:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.80,0:36:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在世界上…有着很多悲伤的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.20,0:36:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法传递的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.05,0:36:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法相互理解的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.22,0:36:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法完成的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.36,0:36:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.14,0:36:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.53,0:36:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.27,0:36:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要守护这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.39,0:36:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护这片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.94,0:36:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.01,0:36:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.97,0:36:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.38,0:36:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.31,0:37:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.21,0:37:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不牺牲任何人的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.70,0:37:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都在寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.22,0:37:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比任何人都更执着地寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.16,0:37:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比任何人都付出更大的牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.54,0:37:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但即使如此还是找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.10,0:37:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很出色了 罗伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.94,0:37:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妈妈…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.76,0:37:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你帮我拯救了那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.48,0:38:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.96,0:38:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤格德拉希尔
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.49,0:38:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库拉特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.61,0:38:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊德跟你很像
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.33,0:38:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和过去的你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.23,0:38:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了拯救世界而拼命地前进
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.79,0:38:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你和罗伊德之间有着决定性的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.77,0:38:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.20,0:38:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你和我和尤安都是
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.57,0:38:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都放弃了纠正错误
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.58,0:38:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 罗伊德相信着错误是能够纠正的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.35,0:38:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人类 精灵 以及两者之间的种族
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.37,0:38:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都能平等生活的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.65,0:38:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确地继承玛天露遗志的人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.71,0:39:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今不是我们 而是罗伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.05,0:39:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听了你们的对话之后 让我确信了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.80,0:39:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够打败他 现在的话能够打败尤格德拉希尔
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.82,0:39:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰大家的热闹真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.05,0:39:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽洛斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.46,0:39:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.48,0:39:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没听说过大树底下好乘凉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.54,0:39:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要背叛同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.15,0:39:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来就是克鲁西斯的间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.95,0:39:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说同伴让我情何以堪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.25,0:39:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的 这是骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.09,0:39:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.80,0:40:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是个半吊子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.42,0:40:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能愉快地活着就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.23,0:40:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是文化和文明都不相同的两个世界合在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.09,0:40:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才让人头疼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.17,0:40:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那岂不毁了神子大人的快乐生活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.83,0:40:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看错你了 神子
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.28,0:40:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很散漫 但我还一直当你是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.91,0:40:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.49,0:40:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.43,0:40:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都想不通
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.39,0:40:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是半吊子
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.45,0:40:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但为什么一直装作半吊子
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.67,0:40:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是有苦衷吧 说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.00,0:41:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你傻了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.17,0:41:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯蕾特
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.32,0:41:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该走了 尤格德拉希尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.86,0:41:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.93,0:41:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯蕾特
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.83,0:41:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯蕾特
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.10,0:41:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 我知道他们去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.07,0:41:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪利斯·卡兰
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.56,0:41:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在于遥远的天之一方
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.24,0:41:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤格德拉希尔的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.31,0:42:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他应该在那里策划着玛天露的复活
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.29,0:46:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽洛斯就由我来好好教训
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.86,0:46:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.36,0:46:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来不会再失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.34,0:46:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挡在你前面的家伙 我会全力驱除他们
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.37,0:46:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再让克鲁西斯任意妄为了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.63,0:46:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊德的背后就由我来守护
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.51,0:46:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再迷惘 援护就交给我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.15,0:46:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.97,0:46:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不跟他说点什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.85,0:46:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊德不需要现在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.65,0:46:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我还有必须要做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.03,0:46:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.15,0:46:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.74,0:46:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到迪利斯·卡兰去
